lead_paragraph: Michigan coach Jim Harbaugh suggested on Twitter that Tennessee coach Butch Jones should focus on his own team instead of tweeting about having lunch in Florida, where the Wolverines are holding spring practice this week at the IMG Academy.

headline.print_headline: Harbaugh to Tennessee's Butch Jones: Focus on Your Team
